Revision history for Perl extension GitLab::API::v3.

0.03      2014-11-18
 - Point the user at the Constants module from the main docs.
 - Add a CONTRIBUTING section to the docs describing how v3.pm
   is generated.
 - Add an author/README.pod to explain how the module generation
   works.
 - Add an EXCEPTIONS section to the docs explaing how exception
   handling it done.
 - Log stuff using Log::Any.
 - Added a SEE ALSO section with reference to Net::GitLab.

0.02      2014-11-18
 - Implement the entire API (wew!).

0.01      2014-11-16
 - First release.

